        <item>
            <title>Tesla 全新 Model 3 Performance 接受訂購   Elon Musk：快過保時捷 911</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/24/new-tesla-model-3-performance/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=new-tesla-model-3-performance</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/24/new-tesla-model-3-performance/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:32:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3 Performance]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231061</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Tesla 宣佈今日推出 Model 3 Performance，現已於 Tesla 官方網站接受訂購，「一換一」計劃後價格為 HK$396,880。Elon Musk 早前更在 X（前稱 Twitter）表示，新 Model 3 Performance 比保時捷 911 更快。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436945581_4055703190-694x455.png" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436945581_4055703190-694x455.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436945581_4055703190.png 1206w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Model 3 Performance 是 Model 3 的升級版本，無論裏外均有不少升級，以配合「Ludicrous」高性能模式。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231067" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_59-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_59-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_59-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Ludicrous 模式曾在 2016 至 2021 年間生產的 Model S 及 Model X Performance 版本中提供。Model 3 Performance 使用最新的技術，僅需 3.1 秒即可由靜止起步加速至時速 100 公里，並在單次充電下提供 528 公里續航距離（WLTP）。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231068" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_52-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_52-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_52-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Model 3 Performance 配備帶有 Ludicrous 標誌的全新前座椅、全新且更大的後尾翼，以及全新的自動適應減震系統，以增強整體駕駛體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231069" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_64-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_64-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_64-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲帶有 Ludicrous 標誌的全新前座椅</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231070" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_83-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_83-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_83-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新且更大的後尾翼</p><p>Model 3 Performance 配備了新的運動型座椅。新座椅支撐力更強，而且形狀和結構在轉彎和動態駕駛過程中可以提供更多側向支撐之餘，亦保持日常駕駛的便利性和舒適性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231074" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_92-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_92-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_92-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231075" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_93-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_93-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_93-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="block block-layout-builder block-inline-blockrich-text"></div><div></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231080" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_91-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_91-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_91-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231076" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_60-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_60-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_60-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231077" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_88-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_88-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_88-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231078" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_89-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_89-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_89-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy"