yle="text-align: center;">▲紅色卡鉗</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231066" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_97-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_97-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_97-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲帶有 Ludicrous 標誌的車尾箱</p><p>Model 3 Perfomance「一換一」計劃後價格為 HK$396,880。任何全新 Model 3 或 Model Y 的新車車主，如果他們的住所允許並符合家用充電設施的條件，可以免費獲得到價值高達 HK$18,800 的 Tesla 掛牆式充電器。</p><h2>Model 3 規格</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 168px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 48px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 48px;"></td><td style="width: 25%; height: 48px; text-align: center;">Model 3</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 48px; text-align: center;">Model 3 長續航</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 48px; text-align: center;">Model 3 Performance</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">續航距離（WLTP）</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">513 公里</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">629 公里</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">528 公里</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">最高時速</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">201 公里／小時</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">201 公里／小時</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">261 公里／小時</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">加速（0-100 公里／小時）</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">6.1 秒</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">4.4 秒</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">3.1 秒</td></tr><tr style="height: 48px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 48px;">價格（「一換一」計劃後）</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 48px; text-align: center;">HK$270,200</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 48px; text-align: center;">HK$344,635</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 48px; text-align: center;">HK$396,880</td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;<br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/24/tesla-1q-profit-falls-55-moves-to-speed-production-of-cheaper-vehicles/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla 第一季盈利跌 55%   將提早推出更實惠新車款</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/20/tesla-s-y-x-price-cut/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla Y/S/X 美國減價 2000 美元  Model Y 重返美國有史以來最低價</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/20/tesla-recalls-all-3878-cybertrucks/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla Cybertruck 油門有機會卡住　近 4,000 部全數需要召回維修</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/24/new-tesla-model-3-performance/life-tech/auto/">Tesla 全新 Model 3 Performance 接受訂購   Elon Musk：快過保時捷 911</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
